skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pelicans radio
des:
Plays Pelicans match broadcasts from Radio Voima during the matches. In times when there is no game going on, play the normal Radio Voima (www.radiovoima.fi) radio channel.

For example, you can start by saying "Alexa, open Pelicans Radio", then say "Play" to begin listening. Say "Alexa, Stop" to stop listening.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
